# UI / Design System

Implements: ADR-004 (design system). Page/Inertia patterns ‚Üí `frontend.mdc`.

## Tokens & styling

- Tailwind 4 via `resources/css/app.css` + `retailpulse.css` ‚Äî **no** `tailwind.config.js`
- Prefer OKLch / `text-rp-*` / `border-rp-border` tokens over ad hoc hex
- Light **and** dark theme must work ‚Äî do not style for one theme only
- Prefer Tailwind + existing tokens; do not add new CSS files unless necessary
- Icons: `lucide-react`

## Component layers

| Use | For |
| :--- | :--- |
| `@/Components/ui/*` | Button, Dialog, Select, Table, Input, ‚Ä¶ |
| `@/Components/common/*` | PageHeader, FormCard, FormInfoPanel, AdminFormField, ModalHeader, DataTable, ScrollArea |
| `@/Components/admin/*` | Domain-specific composites |

## Buttons

- Primary: `Button variant="brand"` / `.rp-btn-primary` ‚Äî **black at rest, teal on hover** (`bg-ink-900` ‚Üí `hover:bg-teal-500`; dark: teal rest ‚Üí lighter hover)
- Never solid teal/green at rest on primary actions
- Change the shared `buttonVariants` / `.rp-btn-primary` definition if the convention must change ‚Äî do not override per page with `bg-teal-*`
- Outline cancel: `variant="outline"`; destructive flows confirm via `useConfirm()` ‚Äî never `window.confirm()`

## Forms

- Fields: `AdminFormField` + `rp-form-input`; pass `required` for asterisk
- Checkboxes: `rp-checkbox-label` + `accent-teal-600` ‚Äî never a bare unstyled checkbox
- Dedicated create pages: `FormCard` (`xl:col-span-2`) + `FormInfoPanel` (`xl:col-span-1`); actions **inside** FormCard footer (`flex justify-end gap-3 border-t ‚Ä¶`), not under the info column
- Section headers: `rp-section-title` distinct from `PageHeader`

## Modals

- Always `ModalHeader` (icon + title + optional description + close) ‚Äî never a bare `<h3>`
- Default field layout: `grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2`; single column only for small modals
- Past ~8 fields: section with `rp-section-title` + `border-t border-rp-border pt-4`
- Long bodies: `ScrollArea` (below) ‚Äî never raw `overflow-y-auto` on a bare div/form
- Footer: `flex justify-end gap-2 border-t ‚Ä¶` ‚Äî outline cancel + brand submit
- Width: `md` ‚â§6 fields ¬∑ `xl`/`2xl` for 7‚Äì16 in 2 cols ¬∑ `3xl` for denser/repeatable grids

## Scrollable regions

Any `overflow-y-auto` / `overflow-x-auto` region uses `@/Components/common/ScrollArea` (themed `rp-scroll`). Call sites supply `max-h-*` / overflow via `className`. Use `as="form"` when the scroll region is the form. POS may also use `pos-scroll`.

## Tables & typography

- Tabular layouts: `@/Components/ui/table` over raw `<table>` when building new UI
- Muted copy: `rp-text-muted`; match spacing/typography of the nearest existing admin page
- Responsive: layouts must work on desktop and mobile; WCAG 2.1 AA via Radix primitives

## Cards

- Prefer existing `FormCard` / page patterns over inventing new card chrome
- Do not introduce one-off shadow/radius systems that diverge from `rp-*` tokens
